{"tid":2245676,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《香港自治法》報告列制裁原因：林鄭押後選舉  美警告大行勿與10官交易","createTime":"2020-10-16T11:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T13:18:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e450d6d250d05525ac82fbb645b8b7440fd641b8","tid":2245676,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:45:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/LBFC3N43U5GY5POWKWQIXKKAWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FLBFC3N43U5GY5POWKWQIXKKAWM%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU1Df25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=ee25b15e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FLBFC3N43U5GY5POWKWQIXKKAWM%2F&h=01c5dffd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/LBFC3N43U5GY5POWKWQIXKKAWM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n《香港自治法》報告列制裁原因：林鄭押後選舉 <br />\n美警告大行勿與10官交易<br />\n<br />\n【中美角力】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：盧偉聰「甩名」發聲明： 料無被剔除<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國國務院前日向國會提交首份《香港自治法》報告，點名10位損害香港自治的中港官員，包括特首林鄭月娥和港區國安委秘書長陳國基等人，指他們很大程度上促成中國未有根據《中英聯合聲明》及《基本法》履行其義務。國務院警告國際金融機構勿與受制裁人士交易，否則可能面對嚴厲制裁。<br />\n<br />\n跟美國財政部8月公佈的11人制裁名單比較，..............................<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：建制派傳被禁晤「五眼」官<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/b9mSn2cVP_T0yvwkKEDr5nHlIw8=/1775x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OKKIGIFAS5BFLBZVLO4B77UU6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fb9mSn2cVP_T0yvwkKEDr5nHlIw8%3D%2F1775x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOKKIGIFAS5BFLBZVLO4B77UU6Q.jpg&h=cc568516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參議員指失擴大力度良機<br />\n<br />\n此外，報告指國務卿及財長須在60天內向國會提交與這10人進行大額交易的金融機構清單，並由總統下令制裁相關機構。制裁方式有10項，包括禁止銀行業務交易、制裁機構行政人員等（見附表），..........................<br />\n<br />\n.................................；北京透過施行港版國安法，癱瘓香港民主制度、人權、司法獨立及個人自由。美國已多次公開譴責北京與港府大規模逮捕示威者、因政治因素延後舉辦立法會選舉等行徑。<br />\n<br />\n但有份草擬《香港自治法》的美國民主黨參議員范霍倫（Chris Van Hollen）認為，今次報告錯失了可擴大制裁個人或機構力度的良機。他說：.........................<br />\n<br />\n............................，影響香港人嘅權利，但綜觀其他世界地方選舉都可以如期舉行，真正嘅目的係因為疫情押後，定係因為其他原因？呢個可能成為其中一被制裁嘅罪名。」<br />\n<br />\n至於警務處長鄧炳強被制裁的「罪名」，包括在港版國安法生效後24小時內，拘捕10名民主派人士。...........................<br />\n<br />\n................................，佢就真係『嚟真』，金融機構要判斷風險，一旦向這類人士提供服務，佢自己都可能會覺得好煩，可能要佢哋（被制裁人士）『過主』。」<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部表示，如果美國堅持走上錯誤的道路，中國會採取反制措施。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府回應指，美國近月越來越明目張膽地干預香港事務。對美國當局發表報告，當中對香特別行政區作出毫無根據和不負責任的指控，..........................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wnvtLu5iWVXoO-UJqEyIR8AfcGw=/1991x2406/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B2VH2F3TOJFZZPPRL2DOB6K3XI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwnvtLu5iWVXoO-UJqEyIR8AfcGw%3D%2F1991x2406%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB2VH2F3TOJFZZPPRL2DOB6K3XI.gif&h=d7b7c9f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/990XNKzTYXLMHufACn02hmKu2c4=/599x1011/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NEHFKUWNVBEEFDEIEPXSBFIRJI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F990XNKzTYXLMHufACn02hmKu2c4%3D%2F599x1011%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNEHFKUWNVBEEFDEIEPXSBFIRJI.gif&h=1e8c7933&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"684ca6438ea1bc948e14089fb33c133c4523c9f6","tid":2245676,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"林鄭：等多幾個月拜登上場，參眾兩院都係民主黨控制，驚條鐵咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7093e0d58b08150aa37327fd730821625f92cb28","tid":2245676,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925d6e0a42fb72aeb11171dfd5abfc3ea7cc91f8","tid":2245676,"uid":81214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"684ca6438ea1bc948e14089fb33c133c4523c9f6","tid":2245676,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"林鄭：等多幾個月拜登上場，參眾兩院都係民主黨控制，驚條鐵咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"個仔繼續讀博士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d4307c22f9c5323457d80f8a30f11467feed42","tid":2245676,"uid":201605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"其實依然係制裁11個人<br />\n今次個名單得10個人係因為盧偉聰資料冇更新<br />\n個名單係更新資料嚟<br />\n寫到明係update，乜乜to乜乜<br />\n個記者自己唔睇清楚網上話乜就信乜係咁話10個"},{"pid":"6e75a2ab87bdd4b51dad67324909b241960729c6","tid":2245676,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://home.treasury.gov/policy-issues/financial-sanctions/recent-actions/20201014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.treasury.gov%2Fpolicy-issues%2Ffinancial-sanctions%2Frecent-actions%2F20201014&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU1Df25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=6b2e9e65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://home.treasury.gov/policy-issues/financial-sanctions/recent-actions/20201014</a>"}]}